platformOrApplicationFailedToLoadError.comment: An error to show when the applicaiton or the platform code fails to load. The {0} placeholder is the platform package name and the {1} placeholder is the applicatio name.

applicationFailedToInitializeError.comment: An error to show when the applicaiton fails to initialize. The {0} placeholder is the error.

applicationFailedToLoadError.comment: An error to show when the applicaiton fails to load. The {0} placeholder is the application name and the {1} placeholder is the error.

invalidManifestError.comment: An error to show when the applicaiton manifest is invalid. The {0} placeholder is the application manifest ID.

invaliPreloadedDataError.comment: An error to show when the preloaded data is invalid.

manifestNotFoundError.comment: An error to show when the manifest could not be found. The {0} placeholder is the manifest identifier.

debugManifestLoadingWarning.comment: A warnings to show to the user when they're attempting to load debug scripts.
debugManifestLoadingWarning.value: WARNING: This page is requesting to load unsafe scripts, which could potentially harm your computer! Do not proceed unless you trust the developer and understand the risks.\n\nIf you are unsure, click "Cancel."

unableToResolveConfigError.comment: Error to show when a manifest module's config cannot be found. The {0} placeholder is the module's identifier.
unableToResolveConfigError.value: Unable to resolve config for module "{0}".

invalidFrameworkModuleError.comment: Error to show when an invalid framework module is specified. The {0} placeholder is the module's identifier.

missingDeveloperToolsTabInitFunctionErro.comment: Error to show when the component loader function is missing in a registered DeveloperToolsTab.

closeDeveloperToolsAriaLabel.comment: Alternative/accessability text for the developer tools close button.

developerToolsTabLoadingText.comment: Text to show when a developer tools tab is loading.

developerToolsTabLoadingUnknownError.comment: Error text to show when a developer tools fails to load for an unknown reason.
developerToolsTabLoadingUnknownError.value: Unknown error loading developer tools module.

tabTitle.comment: Manifest manager developer tools tab title.

noManifestSelected.comment: Text to show when no manifest is selected in the manifest manager in the developer tools.
